Mingle Macro - Create Defect
============================

Inserts a form into the story markup to quickly create a defect for that story.

* Original code: Ben Butler-Cole, from http://community.thoughtworks.com/posts/97a2c29d6e
* Modified for Crossroads, added unit tests, extended as fully-featured & embeddable form: Nathan B


== Usage

{{ create_defect }}


This will give you a 'CREATE NEW DEFECT' button. When clicked, the button will be replaced with the defect form.

